 />\n<br />\n我做salon既 可以參考下"},{"pid":"cbe0e89fcddfb4852ae5e3e8af42ef5e12be9dce","tid":865282,"uid":136619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10456e974e26964d33fbf67c9df6d53d13087282","tid":865282,"uid":56751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T00:38:19.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有懷疑過係咪要不斷轉洗頭水... 不過我最近發現 每次去完salon, 啲頭髮都可以keep耐好多先洗，隔日先洗都唔油 後來我發覺每次吹頭都分好多個section去吹，頭皮一定要吹乾透，個頭會冇咁易油。吹頭前後可加少少髮尾油/olive oil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:29:24.000Z","msg":"係呀係呀，我仲試過買2支唔同牌子嘅洗頭水輪著用，不過最後又係過左排之後，2支洗完都係頭痕加頭皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad91f26d3a446b5335da138c5533f7c5a7d55a0c","tid":865282,"uid":136619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f58ade7cf1266fd89e26d28be4325e5052bd15d","tid":865282,"uid":57594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"呢個都搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e51bf0b7360e55b25f67d54b2ccb1f782cfed8","tid":865282,"uid":136619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"308823fb185d8a84f5a543b35db84c57ab4a55a9","tid":865282,"uid":26215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2e3c13b6805712a6f4514707636d0ca22b3e249e","tid":865282,"uid":136619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T02:23:26.000Z","msg":"有無人同我一樣，揾極都揾唔啱洗頭水？<br />\n通常一換洗頭水頭，頭2個星期都好地地，<br />\n用完頭髮好順滑，好乾爽，<br />\n但用耐少少，d頭髮就開始毛躁，頭頂易油，又痕又有頭皮<br />\n換左好多隻牌子都係咁<br />\n已經簡無矽個d<br />\n仲可以點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:53:43.000Z",